<h1>Letter Before Claim</h1>
<p><strong>{{brand_name}}</strong></p>
<p><em>{{claim_label}}</em></p>

<hr>

<p><strong>From:</strong> {{claimant_name}}<br>{{claimant_address}}{{#if claimant_email}}<br>{{claimant_email}}{{/if}}{{#if claimant_phone}}<br>{{claimant_phone}}{{/if}}</p>
<p><strong>To:</strong> {{defendant_name}}<br>{{defendant_address}}{{#if defendant_email}}<br>{{defendant_email}}{{/if}}</p>
<p><strong>Date:</strong> {{generation_date}}</p>

<h2>Dear {{defendant_name}}</h2>

<p>
  This is a letter before claim. {{claimant_name}} says that you owe
  {{currency total_claim_amount}} in relation to the following dispute:
</p>

<p>{{claim_summary}}</p>

{{#if category_context}}
<h2>Background</h2>
<p>{{category_context}}</p>
{{/if}}

<h2>Legal basis being relied on</h2>
<p>{{legal_rules.legal_basis}}</p>

<h2>Amount claimed</h2>
<table border="1" cellpadding="8" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <th align="left">Item</th>
    <th align="left">Amount</th>
  </tr>
  {{#each line_items}}
  <tr>
    <td>{{description}}</td>
    <td>{{currency amount}}</td>
  </tr>
  {{/each}}
  <tr>
    <td><strong>Total claimed before court fee</strong></td>
    <td><strong>{{currency total_claim_amount}}</strong></td>
  </tr>
</table>

{{#if claim_interest}}
<p>
  The claimant also wants interest considered. The daily interest figure currently recorded for review is
  {{currency daily_interest}} per day at {{interest_rate}}% per year.
</p>
{{/if}}

<h2>Pre-action position</h2>
<p>{{pre_action_summary}}</p>
{{#if pre_action_sent_date}}
<p><strong>Most recent demand sent:</strong> {{pre_action_sent_date}}</p>
{{/if}}
{{#if response_deadline}}
<p><strong>Response deadline given:</strong> {{response_deadline}}</p>
{{/if}}
<p>{{legal_rules.pre_action_rule}}</p>

<h2>What is required now</h2>
<p>
  Please pay the amount claimed, make a clear written proposal, or explain why you dispute the claim.
  {{#if response_deadline}}Please respond by {{response_deadline}}.{{/if}}
  If the matter is not resolved, the claimant may issue a county court money claim using the attached
  particulars, schedule of loss, evidence index, and Form N1.
</p>

<p><strong>Signed:</strong> _________________________ {{claimant_name}}</p>
